---
title: Cheddar-Crusted Turkey Breast with Sweet Potato Mash and Zucchini
description: Tonight's menu features cheddar-crusted turkey, sweet potato mash and roasted zucchini. The best part? Everything comes together in 30 minutes! Talk about a dinnertime win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1003_W23_CA_RC152191-10_MAIN_low-c3f4c5c1.jpg
